but has a magnitude equal to one.

396
00:18:21,000 --> 00:18:25,000
Or something that is not decreasing.

397
00:18:25,000 --> 00:18:27,000
It has a magnitude equal to one.

398
00:18:27,000 --> 00:18:28,000
All right?

399
00:18:28,000 --> 00:18:32,000
It's an exponential of i times something, right?

