00:18:39,000 --> 00:18:41,000
Not minimizing it.

404
00:18:41,000 --> 00:18:43,000
You're summing over all trajectories.

405
00:18:43,000 --> 00:18:50,000
You're just summing over all of these amplitude, okay.

