01:00:19,054 --> 01:00:20,054
But the expansion of e to the i something,

1292
01:00:20,054 --> 01:00:22,054
of course, this is just an expansion

1293
01:00:22,054 --> 01:00:24,054
of e to the i something or other,

1294
01:00:24,054 --> 01:00:26,054
so of course it converges.

1295
01:00:26,054 --> 01:00:27,054
No, no, no, no, no, no, no.

