01:00:27,054 --> 01:00:30,054
But the sum over configurations doesn't have to converge.

1297
01:00:30,054 --> 01:00:32,054
Yeah.

1298
01:00:32,054 --> 01:00:34,054
This part converges.

1299
01:00:34,054 --> 01:00:37,054
And this is going to be

1300
01:00:37,054 --> 01:00:40,054
some finite number of total configurations considered.

1301
01:00:40,054 --> 01:00:42,054
Yeah.

1302
01:00:42,054 --> 01:00:44,054
Okay.

1303
01:00:44,054 --> 01:00:46,554
Let's, let me, all right, now let's

