01:01:54,054 --> 01:01:58,054
This corresponds to a graph

1331
01:01:58,054 --> 01:02:00,054
where you start a particle in here,

1332
01:02:00,054 --> 01:02:02,054
and it goes to here.

1333
01:02:02,054 --> 01:02:04,054
That's this factor.

1334
01:02:04,054 --> 01:02:06,054
And the other factor, instead of

1335
01:02:06,054 --> 01:02:08,054
taking the particle that's already there

1336
01:02:08,054 --> 01:02:10,054
and moving it over here,

1337
01:02:10,054 --> 01:02:11,554
it just takes a totally new

1338
01:02:11,554 --> 01:02:13,054
particle and moves it to here.

1339
01:02:13,054 --> 01:02:14,054
Okay.

1340
01:02:14,054 --> 01:02:17,054
So this same factor, this same term,

