01:02:59,054 --> 01:03:05,054
Because every starting, every dangling endpoint here,

1357
01:03:05,054 --> 01:03:08,054
well, let's see.

1358
01:03:08,054 --> 01:03:12,054
Yeah, it has to end somewhere.

1359
01:03:12,054 --> 01:03:13,554
